      <li>N. Mardirossian and M. Head-Gordon, <a class="ink-link" href="https://doi.org/10.1063/1.4952647">"ωB97M-V: A combinatorially optimized, range-separated hybrid, meta-GGA density functional with VV10 nonlocal correlation,"</a> <em>J. Chem. Phys.</em> 144, 214110 (2016). <span class="src-note">— the functional that labeled OMol25.</span></li>
